h shall her name be’). This has been one of the most enduringly popular girls' names."],"variants":[{"name":"Sara","meanings":["Variant of   Sarah .  This is the form used in the Greek of the New Testament (Hebrews 11:11)."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sarah Swainson was born in 1344, in Hawkshead, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Richard Dixon. She died in 1388, in Cumbria, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 44."},"et":{"1344–1388":"1344–1388","1332–1393":"1332–1393","1367–1447":"1367–1447","1447":"1447","1367":"1367","1344":"1344","1388":"1388","1332":"1332","1393":"1393","Cumbria, England, United Kingdom":"Cumbria, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Hawkshead, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hawkshead, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1344–1388":"1344–1388","1332–1393":"1332–1393","1367–1447":"1367–1447","1447":"1447","1367":"1367","1344":"1344","1388":"1388","1332":"1332","1393":"1393","Cumbria, England, United Kingdom":"Cumbria, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"England","Hawkshead, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hawkshead, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1344–1388":"1344–1388","1332–1393":"1332–1393","1367–1447":"1367–1447","1447":"1447","1367":"1367","1344":"1344","1388":"1388","1332":"1332","1393":"1393","Cumbria, England, United Kingdom":"Cumbria, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England":"Angleterre","Hawkshead, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom":"Hawkshead, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Sarah Swainson est née en 1344, à Hawkshead, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Richard Dixon. Elle est décédée en 1388, à Cumbria, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 44 ans."},"de":{"1344–1388":"1344–1388","1332–1393":"1332–1393","1367–1447":"1367–1447","1447":"1447","1367":"1367","1344":"1344","1388":"1388","1332":"1332","1393":"1393","Cumbria, England, United Kingdom":"Cumbria, England, United Kingdom","England":"Engl